# Astro-first deploy
#
# Astro static HTML serves all marketing/public routes. The React SPA
# (admin, portal, proposal-sign) is NOT bundled into this dist yet —
# see progress.txt "admin/portal migration status" for the plan to move
# it to admin.ascendsystems.ai before the public Astro site goes live.
#
# Once the React SPA is being co-deployed, uncomment the lines below
# (and add `dist/admin/index.html` + `dist/portal/index.html` to the
# build pipeline) so client-side routing inside the SPA works:
#
# /admin/*       /admin/index.html       200
# /portal/*      /portal/index.html      200
# /proposals/*   /admin/index.html       200
